#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:1827
msgid ""
"You can create as many styles as you wish for a layer but only one can be"
" active at a time. In combination with :ref:`Map Themes <map_themes>`, "
"this offers a quick and powerful way to manage complex projects without "
"the need to duplicate any layer in the map legend."
