#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:1854
msgid "Save as text file"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/introduction/general_tools.rst:1856
msgid ""
"Clicking the |selectString| :menuselection:`Style --> Save Style`, you "
"can save the style as a:"
